abstract: >-
  A private-sector economic operating system designed to bridge the systemic 'Trust Deficit.' NUPA-LR restores Community Sovereignty through the perpetual 
  licensing of underutilized state land (via the Land Rights Act of 2018), hard-codes an 80/20 anti-leakage 
  revenue waterfall, and creates a market-based firewall against AI youth-job displacement—all at 
  $0.00 taxpayer cost.
